<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="beautiful-adj">beautiful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bjuːtɪfl/    美 /'bjuːtɪfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-ugly">1.★ <strong>美丽的；漂亮的【反：ugly】；极好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a beautiful voice 
美妙的嗓音</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is beautiful. 
她很漂亮。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— How was the game? 
比赛怎么样？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Beautiful!
棒极了！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>beautifully /'bju:tɪfli/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You play the piano beautifully. 
你钢琴弹得好极了。</p></div></div>